其 1,050/1,000 MB/s 的读/写速度应该足以满足大多数人的需求。</p><h2>三星980 Pro </h2><p><core-commerce id="9f078a0fd20d45f5aedbda94f3d9998c" data-type="product-list"></core-commerce></p><p> <a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;cpos:24;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsInN0b3JlSWQiOiI2NmVhNTY3YS1jOTg3LTRjMmUtYTJmZi0wMjkwNGVmZGU2ZWEiLCJsYW5kaW5nVXJsIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYW1hem9uLmNvbS9kcC9CMDhHTFg3VE5UP3RhZz1nZGd0MGMtcC1vLTFwbS0yMCIsImNvbnRlbnRVdWlkIjoiMmUwYjg1YzQtZDU2Yi00Nzc1LTkyNGItNmIyY2U1MzBhNzExIn0&amp;signature=AQAAAQD4NC5Qvng0Fs_tZTJKb8CB7rCUtKocT3JZDj8Eox5m&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2Fdp%2FB08GLX7TNT" data-demonetize-referrer="https://www.amazon.com/dp/B08GLX7TNT?th=1" class="rapid-with-clickid">三星980 Pro SSD</a>已跌至50美元，创下新低。对于 PS5 来说，这是另一个不错的选择，特别是如果你愿意的话，你可以选择带有散热器的型号。 980 Pro 的读取速度高达 7,000 MB/s 和可靠的热控制。</p><h2>英睿达 MX500 </h2><p><core-commerce id="cbe56645c9ff429695ee018793e3be0d" data-type="product-list"></core-commerce></p><p> <a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;cpos:25;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsInN0b3JlSWQiOiI2NmVhNTY3YS1jOTg3LTRjMmUtYTJmZi0wMjkwNGVmZGU2ZWEiLCJsYW5kaW5nVXJsIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYW1hem9uLmNvbS9kcC9CMDc4NlFOUzlCLz90YWc9Z2RndDBjLXAtby0xcG0tMjAiLCJjb250ZW50VXVpZCI6IjJlMGI4NWM0LWQ1NmItNDc3NS05MjRiLTZiMmNlNTMwYTcxMSJ9&amp;signature=AQAAATslz_TXOQq2wZFNLWWAt4BRw6MVj7uimqlOiREaDFVr&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2Fdp%2FB0786QNS9B%2F" data-demonetize-referrer="https://www.amazon.com/dp/B0786QNS9B/?th=1" class="rapid-with-clickid">Crucial 的 MX500</a>内置硬盘在亚马逊上折扣价仅为 48 美元。它的顺序读取速度为 56