容，并支持 AirPlay 2 和使用耳机进行私人聆听。</p><h2>谷歌 Pixel 7a </h2><p><core-commerce id="df64cb2397694fb6b5e5537076438d29" data-type="product-list"></core-commerce></p><p> <a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;cpos:29;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsInN0b3JlSWQiOiI2NmVhNTY3YS1jOTg3LTRjMmUtYTJmZi0wMjkwNGVmZGU2ZWEiLCJsYW5kaW5nVXJsIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYW1hem9uLmNvbS9kcC9CMEJaOVhOQlJCP3RhZz1nZGd0MGMtcC1vLTFwbS0yMCIsImNvbnRlbnRVdWlkIjoiMmUwYjg1YzQtZDU2Yi00Nzc1LTkyNGItNmIyY2U1MzBhNzExIn0&amp;signature=AQAAAZdaBFLB-Ahof3YN2aCDcywk9K2CpFe-s_n5pm9DV10p&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2Fdp%2FB0BZ9XNBRB" data-demonetize-referrer="https://www.amazon.com/dp/B0BZ9XNBRB?th=1" class="rapid-with-clickid">Google Pixel 7a</a>目前售价 449 美元，比平时便宜 50 美元，创下历史新低。由于其快速的 Tensor G2 芯片、流畅的 90Hz 显示屏以及对无线充电的支持，这是您现在可以获得<a data-i13n="cpos:30;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/the-engadget-guide-to-the-best-midrange-smartphones-120050366.html">的最好的中端手机</a>。 7a 还配备坚固的摄像头和 IP67 防水设计。</p><h2> Nest <strong>WiFi Pro - 3 件装</strong></h2><p><core-commerce id="fffd5a9dd59d4ab895480eeb53159906" data-type="product-list"></core-commerce></p><p> <a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;cpos:31;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAAWWNiyOPcwh0W_aJm-KPH0PCSQju7IqbwCyB5i2teIG5&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FGoogle-Nest-WiFi-Pro-Reliable%2Fdp%2FB0BCQS55N6" class="rapid-with-clickid">Google Nest WiFi Pro 三件套</a>为您提供与这对产品相同的技术，但范围更广。使用三个路由器，您可以在 6,600 平方英尺的范围内访问 WiFi。三件套产品享受 25% 的折扣，售价为 300 美元，因此每台 Nest WiFi Pro 只需 100 美元——考虑到它们通常的零售价为每台 200 美元，这真是太划算了。至于颜色，全部选择雪色，或者混合使用雪色、雾色和亚麻色。</p><h2>雷蛇猎魂迷你版</h2><p><core-commerce id="39fd7b5804234803adc09589a166e639" data-type="product-list"></core-commerce></p><p>紧凑型<a data-i13n="cpos:32;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAAd2S9ZVEGupLeKU_fxLjP70G3RJDlpZC8MvCrnx69kIN&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FRazer-Huntsman-Mini-Gaming-Keyboard%2Fdp%2FB08BFF4C7J%2F&amp;uuid=x3oFAYDJGNZTkzRN68940">Razer Huntsman Mini</a>现已降至 68 美元，比平时便宜 43%。这两笔交易都不是历史最低价，但过去几个月这两款机型的零售价通常在 80 至 100 美元之间。 Huntsman Mini 是我们<a data-i13n="cpos:33;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/best-60-percent-keyboards-160038272.html">60% 最佳键盘</a>指南中的首选，因为它的按键舒适且对游戏反应始终如一。整个东西感觉做工精良，每个按键都有优质的 PBT 键帽和 RGB 灯光。每个键也可以通过宏进行编程。不过，对于那些喜欢弹性和触感更好的人来说，这里的开关并不理想，而且超紧凑的设计并不适合所有人。</p><h2>罗技 Litra Glow </h2><p><core-commerce id="3e1c4888c81c412693a0ba306c29ea73" data-type="product-list"></core-commerce></p><p>直播主播或任何想要在镜头上看起来更好的人都应该在打折时购买<a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;cpos:34;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsInN0b3JlSWQiOiI2NmVhNTY3YS1jOTg3LTRjMmUtYTJmZi0wMjkwNGVmZGU2ZWEiLCJsYW5kaW5nVXJsIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYW1hem9uLmNvbS9ncC9wcm9kdWN0L0IwOTdRWkdSQ1E_dGFnPWdkZ3QwYy1wLW8tMXBtLTIwIiwiY29udGVudFV1aWQiOiIyZTBiODVjNC1kNTZiLTQ3NzUtOTI0Yi02YjJjZTUzMGE3MTEifQ&amp;signature=AQAAAQ9m3H9rm8IzjhMnPrJaxya75cAH-QFVD5g_MUjc6QC0&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2Fgp%2Fproduct%2FB097QZGRCQ" data-demonetize-referrer="https://www.amazon.com/gp/product/B097QZGRCQ?" class="rapid-with-clickid">罗技的 Litra Glow LED 灯</a>。我们在指南中推荐它，因为 USB 供电的设备可发出漫射、柔和的光芒，没有刺眼的阴影，并配有可扩展的显示器支架。</p><h2>雷蛇灵刃 15 </h2><p><core-commerce id="d3a9d9c682b24277991fdd62df07d2bc" data-type="product-list"></core-commerce></p><p> <a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;cpos:35;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsInN0b3JlSWQiOiI2NmVhNTY3YS1jOTg3LTRjMmUtYTJmZi0wMjkwNGVmZGU2ZWEiLCJsYW5kaW5nVXJsIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYW1hem9uLmNvbS9kcC9CMDlSQkpDOFk5P3RhZz1nZGd0MGMtcC1vLTFwbS0yMCIsImNvbnRlbnRVdWlkIjoiMmUwYjg1YzQtZDU2Yi00Nzc1LTkyNGItNmIyY2U1MzBhNzExIn0&amp;signature=AQAAAUFbzkbnULalqrro4KWHGcYrCSgovwFD9z0MxRUFbvsp&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2Fdp%2FB09RBJC8Y9" data-demonetize-referrer="https://www.amazon.com/dp/B09RBJC8Y9?th=1" class="rapid-with-clickid">Razer Blade 15</a>配备 Core i7-12800H 处理器、GeForce RTX 3070 Ti GPU、240Hz QHD 显示屏、16GB RAM 和 1TB SSD 的配置目前已降至 1,923 美元。这比近几个月的正常市场价格低了约 375 美元。去年我们给 Blade 15 <a data-i13n="cpos:36;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/razer-blade-15-2022-review-a-real-treat-if-youve-got-the-cash-160032467.html">的评分为 86 分</a>，目前我们在<a data-i13n="cpos:37;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/best-gaming-laptops-172033838.html">最佳游戏笔记本电脑</a>指南中将其作为首选推荐。此配置是 2022 年型号 - <a data-i13n="cpos:38;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/razer-updates-the-blade-15-with-13th-gen-intel-cpus-and-rtx-40-series-graphics-190544878.html">最新版本</a>主要是规格提升 - 但它仍然足够强大，可以在高设置和帧速率下玩大多数现代游戏，尤其是使用 DLSS 时。不过，为任何刀片笔记本电脑支付高价的主要原因是因为它采用纤薄且具有优质感觉的铝制设计来提供强大的功能。请注意，它可能会很热，并且电池寿命相当短。</p><p><em>在 Twitter 上</em><em>关注</em><a data-i13n="cpos:39;pos:1" href="https://twitter.com/EngadgetDeals"><em>@EngadgetDeals</em></a>并<a data-i13n="cpos:40;pos:1" href="https://subscription.yahoo.net/Newsletter/Preference/sub?b=engadgetdeals&amp;src"><em>订阅 Engadget Deals 时事通讯，</em></a><em>了解最新的科技交易和购买建议。</em></p>本文最初发表在 Engadget 上：https://www.engadget.com/amazon-prime-day-deals-you-can-still-get-today-123525839.html?src=rss]]>; </description><link/><![CDATA[